title: Audiophile vinyl transfers of some classic rock albums
description:
Here is a collection of classic (NOT classical) albums featuring artists such as Joni Mitchell, David Blue, The Doobie Brothers, Albert King with SRV, Gary Burton, Fred Neil, Iron Butterfly, Melanie, Miles Davis, The Everly Brothers, Billy Joel and San Francisco Ltd. 

These have all been at some time uploaded as one of my torrents, but I am now compiling them under one mega-pack. 

They were sourced using three different turntables-the LEAST of which was a fully Naimed Linn Sondek LP12, all the way up to a fully loaded $30,000 SME30
